\c 14
\s Abhuramu anorwira Roti
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika mumazuva aAmuraferi mambo weShinari, Arioki mambo weErasari, Kedhoriraomeri mambo weEramu, naTidhari, mambo wemarudzi,
\v 2 \add kuti\add* vakaita hondo naBhera mambo weSodhoma, naBhirisha mambo weGomora, Shinabhi mambo weAdhima, naShemebheri mambo weZebhoimi, namambo weBhera, rinova Zoari.
\v 3 Ava vose vakasangana mumupata weSidhimu unova Gungwa reMunyu.
\v 4 Makore gumi nemaviri vakashandira Kedhoriraomeri, asi negore regumi nematatu vaka\add mu\add*mukira.
\v 5 Zvino mugore regumi nemana kwakauya Kedhoriraomeri, nemadzimambo aiva naye, vakarova vaRefaimi paAshitoreti karinaimi, nevaZuzimi paHamu, nevaEmimi paShavhe-kiriataimi,
\v 6 nevaHori pagomo ravo Seiri, kusvikira paEriparani riri pedo nerenje.
\v 7 Zvino vakadzoka vakasvika Enimishipati rinova Kadheshi, ndokurova nyika yose yevaAmareki, nevaAmoriwo, vaigara paHazazoni-Tamari.
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakabuda mambo weSodhoma namambo weGomora, namambo weAdhima namambo weZebhoimi, namambo weBhera ndiro Zoari, vakabuda vakamisa hondo kuzorwa navo pamupata weSidhimu,
\v 9 kurwisana naKedhoriraomeri mambo weEramu, naTidhari mambo wemarudzi, naAmuraferi mambo weShinari, naArioki mambo weErasari; madzimambo mana akamirisana nemadzimambo mashanu.
\v 10 Zvino mupata weSidhimu waiva \add ne\add*makomba etara, uye madzimambo eSodhoma neGomora akatiza, ndokuwiramo; uye vakasara vakatizira kugomo,
\v 11 ndokutora nhumbi dzose dzeSodhoma neGomora, nekudya kwavo kose, ndokuenda.
\v 12 Zvino vakatora Roti, mwanakomana wemunin'ina waAbhuramu nenhumbi dzake, nekuti waigara paSodhoma, ndokuenda.
\p
\v 13 Zvino kwakauya wakange apukunyuka ndokuudza Abhuramu muHebheru, waigara pamiouki* yaMamure muAmori, munin'ina waEshikori nemunin'ina waAneri vakange vaita sungano naAbhuramu.
\v 14 Zvino Abhuramu wakati anzwa kuti hama yake yatapwa, akashongedza zvombo vakange vadzidziswa, vakazvarwa muimba yake, mazana matatu negumi nevasere, ndoku\add va\add*teverera kusvikira paDhani.
\v 15 Zvino wakazvikamura kurwa navo usiku, iye nevaranda vake, ndokuvarova, ndokuvateverera kusvikira paHobha, riri kuruboshwe rweDhamasiko.
\v 16 Zvino wakadzosa nhumbi dzose, naRotiwo hama yake nenhumbi dzake, nevakadziwo nevanhu.
\v 17 Mambo weSodhoma ndokubuda kunosangana naye shure kwekudzoka kunouraya Kedhoraomari nemadzimambo aiva naye pamupata weShavhe unova mupata wamambo.
\v 18 Merikizedheki mambo weSaremi ndokuuisa chingwa newaini; uye iye mupristi waMwari Wekumusoro-soro.
\p
\v 19 Zvino wakamuropafadza ndokuti: Ngaaropafadzwe Abhuramu naMwari Wekumusoro-soro, Muridzi wematenga nepasi.
\p
\v 20 Uye ngaaropafadzwe Mwari Wekumusoro-soro, wakakumikidza vavengi vako mumaoko ako. Ndokumupa chegumi chezvose.
\p
\v 21 Zvino mambo weSodhoma wakati kuna Abhuramu: Ndipe vanhu, asi uzvitorere nhumbi.
\p
\v 22 Abhuramu ndokuti kuna mambo weSodhoma: Ndasimudzira ruoko rwangu kuna Jehovha Mwari Wekumusoro-soro, muridzi wematenga nepasi,
\v 23 ndinoti handingatori kubva kurushinda kusvika kurukanda rweshangu pane chose chaunacho, kuti murege kuzoti: Ini ndakafumisa Abhuramu.
\v 24 Kunze kweizvo chete majaya zvaakadya, nemugove wevarume vakainda neni, Aneri, Eshikori naMamure, ivo ngavatore mugove wavo.
